5. **Homepage regex** (`intent_recognition.py`): `客户.*(?:画像|分布|结构|分层)` — covers 画像/分布/结构/分层 but not 类型
6. **Runtime check**: `raw_intent=None`, mapping resolves to `other`

The earliest divergence is at `intent_api_call` — the LLM model, guided by a narrow prompt and a "prefer other when unclear" rule, classified the query as `other`.

